{"type": "article", "id": 21472, "title": "空中盆栽", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-29T07:34:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 58, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135508vriBjkUNc2l7QCJS.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这个漂浮在半空的盆景可以自己转动，似乎脱离了地心引力，就像在银河系中的行星。植物是用苔藓和火山岩组成，借助了一个磁系统设备，下面是手工制作的陶瓷器皿，可以体验在空中浇水的乐趣。产品来自日本设计团队 Hoshinchu Air Bonsai Garden，目前正在众筹，<a href=\"http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1280002828/air-bonsai-create-your-little-star\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150958rX7uQgUmasAJy1dW.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261509597h1WoAzOlVg0aSXL.jpg\" width=\"680\" height=\"423\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.62205882\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726151001kvEhC9OWMlVor8ej.jpg\" width=\"677\" height=\"682\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.00738552\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726151001n60DblOTziJm43rS.jpg\" width=\"680\" height=\"1497\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"2.20147059\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}